paragraphs.title: Set Credential
Environment clean
Create Training dataset table
paragraphs.text:
%sql
create table kdd_train (
    duration NUMBER,
    protocol_type VARCHAR2(4000),
    service VARCHAR2(4000),
    flag VARCHAR2(4000),
    src_bytes NUMBER,
    dst_bytes NUMBER,
    land VARCHAR2(4000),
    wrong_fragment NUMBER,
    urgent NUMBER,
    hot NUMBER,
    num_failed_logins NUMBER,
    logged_in VARCHAR2(4000),
    num_compromised NUMBER,
    root_shell NUMBER,
    su_attempted NUMBER,
    num_root NUMBER,
    num_file_creations NUMBER,
    num_shells NUMBER,
    num_access_files NUMBER,
    num_outbound_cmds NUMBER,
    is_host_login NUMBER,
    is_guest_login NUMBER,
    count NUMBER,
    srv_count NUMBER,
    serror_rate NUMBER,
    srv_serror_rate NUMBER,
    rerror_rate NUMBER,
    srv_rerror_rate NUMBER,
    same_srv_rate NUMBER,
    diff_srv_rate NUMBER,
    srv_diff_host_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_count NUMBER,
    dst_host_srv_count NUMBER,
    dst_host_same_srv_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_diff_srv_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_same_src_port_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_srv_diff_host_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_serror_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_srv_serror_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_rerror_rate NUMBER,
    dst_host_srv_rerror_rate NUMBER,
    type VARCHAR2(4000),
    nil number
   --id NUMBER GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTITY
);

paragraphs.title: Create Testing dataset table
paragraphs.text:
%sql
CREATE TABLE kdd_test AS (SELECT * FROM kdd_train);

paragraphs.title: Import Training/Test dataset
paragraphs.text:
%script
BEGIN
DBMS_CLOUD.COPY_DATA(
    table_name =>'KDD_TRAIN',
    credential_name =>'CRED_KDD',
    --https://objectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oraclecloud.com/n/italysandbox/b/adwhimport/o/KDDTrain%2B.txt
    file_uri_list =>'https://swiftobjectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oraclecloud.com/v1/italysandbox/adwhimport/KDDTrain%2B.txt',
    format => json_object('delimiter' value ',')
 );
 DBMS_CLOUD.COPY_DATA(
    table_name =>'KDD_TEST',
    credential_name =>'CRED_KDD',
    --https://objectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oraclecloud.com/n/italysandbox/b/adwhimport/o/KDDTest%2B.txt
    file_uri_list =>'https://swiftobjectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oraclecloud.com/v1/italysandbox/adwhimport/KDDTest%2B.txt',
    format => json_object('delimiter' value ',')
 );
END;
